      <p>
        <inline name="agenda item name">Review and implementation of the Concluding Document of the Twelfth Special Session of the General Assembly: United Nations regional centres for peace and disarmament</inline>
      </p>
      <p>
        <docTitle>Resolution adopted by the General Assembly on 7 December 2022</docTitle>
      </p>
      <p xml:space="preserve">
